                        size="1" color="#A8A8A8">
                        <font size="2"
                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">The Office of the Chancellory recognized today, following the results of the Senior Council Election, that Councilors Ailen Goldenfire and Alaythia are both promoted to the rank of War Councilor, with a seat on the War Council and specific charges. Ailen shall serve as an Advisor to the High Council on Military Readiness, and Alaythia shall serve as an Advisor to the High Council on Tactical Strategy. For their new duties, as well as congratulating them on their dedication to our family and continued service in the guild, please join me on the message boards and <b><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/fcouncilofarcanafrm2.showMessage?topicID=116.topic">recognize them for their hard work</a></b>. Thanks!</font>
