                        <font size="2"
                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">Well, yes, there's a Patch Today. The servers went down at 5 am Eastern Time for approximately 10 hours (and will come back up, accordingly, at 3 pm Eastern Time). Of course, checking the EQ news forums and the Patch Server itself - there doesn't appear to be any patch to download, much less a patch message to tell us what it was about, so this is likely a server-side patch at this stage, but we'll see. (Update: But I just found off of EverQuest.com a <b><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/fcouncilofarcanafrm2.showMessage?topicID=104.topic">detailed patch message</a></b> that tells you what's new. ;-)) While the patch is in progress, we invite members to please <b><a href="http://www.councilofarcana.com/ledger.html">update your member profiles</a></b>, and visit the <b><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/bcouncilofarcana">message forums</a></b>.</font>
