                        size="1" color="#A8A8A8">
                        <font size="2"
                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">The High Council of the Council of Arcana, after weeks of deliberations, recognized Senior Councilor Khelbun Arunson as a new High Councilor-Designate, granting him a seat upon the highest body of our guild's leadership. Arch Chancellor Kaelon Xerxentis and Arch Chancelloress Allanna Xerxentis, with First Speaker Penroc Riversong, presided over the public ceremony late last night before the entire guild, recognizing Khelbun Arunson as a High Councilor. Please <b><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/fcouncilofarcanafrm2.showMessage?topicID=90.topic">join me in congratulating Khelbun</a></b> and welcoming him as the newest member of the policy-making team in the Council of Arcana. Congratulations, High Councilor Khelbun Arunson!</font>
                        <hr size="1" color="#A8A8A8">
                        <font size="2"
                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">


	<b><a href="http://www.councilofarcana.com/news/talkback/985121336,72763,.shtml">Comments (0)</a></b>
	


</font>
