                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">Today is Patch Day. The servers went down at 3 am PST for 9 hours, which means that they will be back at 12 pm PST / 3 pm EST - or sooner. This patch includes numerous changes - including Epic Quest changes, Fear/Hate upgrades, a new zone, and much more - check out the <b><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/fcouncilofarcanafrm2.showMessage?topicID=83.topic">patch details</a></b> (and keep an eye out for Trux's latest upgrade!). <br><br><b>During patch:</b> Members should check into the <b><a href="http://www.councilofarcana.com/ledger.html">Council Ledger</a></b> and update their character profiles and details. New members (or members that have yet to add their profiles) should add their characters to the ledger, following on the on-screen instructions. Creation passwords can be found on the message boards, or, alternatively, you can use the standard creation password found on the add a character page. <b>ALSO...</b> be sure to check out the <b><a href="http://www.councilofarcana.com/medals.html">Medals Program</a></b>, just announced yesterday. (Also, read the <b><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/fcouncilofarcanafrm2.showMessage?topicID=82.topic">medals announcement</a></b> for feedback and more info.)<br><br><b>After patch:</b> We're considering having <b><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/fcouncilofarcanafrm21.showMessage?topicID=70.topic">an event</a></b> after the patch. Please check it out. Let's have fun this patch day! =)</font>
