                        Tuesday, March 13, 2001 - 4:22 PM EST - <a href="http://www.councilofarcana.com/cgi-forum/ubbmisc.cgi?action=sendthread&thread=http://www.councilofarcana.com/news/viewnews.cgi?newsid$newsid&Subject=Medals System Announced"><img src="http://www.councilofarcana.com/news/envelope.gif" alt="E-mail Medals System Announced" border=0></a> <a href="http://www.councilofarcana.com/news/viewnews.cgi?newsid$newsid" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.councilofarcana.com/news/printer.gif" alt="Print Medals System Announced" border=0></a> </font><hr
                        size="1" color="#A8A8A8">
                        <font size="2"
                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">Today, Arch Chancellor Kaelon Xerxentis announced the implementation of a new <b><a href="http://www.councilofarcana.com/medals.html">Medals System</a></b>, a program that recognizes initiative, leadership, and merit in the Council of Arcana through the creation of chivalric orders and the designation of publicly visible accolaides. Recipients of Medals will be listed in the <b><a href="http://www.councilofarcana.com/heroes.html">Hall of Heroes</a></b>. Please feel free to <b><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/fcouncilofarcanafrm2.showMessage?topicID=82.topic">read the full announcement</a></b>.</font>
