                        size="1" color="#A8A8A8">
                        <font size="2"
                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">On the first attempt, the Council of Arcana and companions defeated Lord Nagafen in a raid, with less than twenty-four hours to prepare. The raid was commanded by Arch Chancellor Kaelon Xerxentis and Arch Chancelloress Allanna Xerxentis, Commander of Tactics was Trex Goldenknight, Buff Leader was High Councilor Sorren Sappho. Special thanks to the many that participated to make the raid very successful and extremely enjoyable. Screenshots and dragon drops forthcoming. </font>
