                        size="1" color="#A8A8A8">
                        <font size="2"
                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">Last night, in a flurry of active adventuring and impromptu raiding, the Council of Arcana defeated the Tangrin (aka "King Kong") in a formal raid. After this success, it immediately pursued various other adventures - including defeating various key mobs for Clarisse's Enchantress Epic Quests and pursuing the Human Skeleton in Karnor Castle, while also clearing most of the castle itself. Congratulations are in order for all of those that participated! Please check our Events Forum for other upcoming formal events, and be ready for impromptu raiding at any given time! Special thanks to Senior Councilor Laer and Arch Chancelloress Allanna Xerxentis for leading last night's festivities.</font>
