                        Monday, December 18, 2000 - 3:31 AM EST - <a href="http://www.councilofarcana.com/cgi-forum/ubbmisc.cgi?action=sendthread&thread=http://www.councilofarcana.com/news/viewnews.cgi?newsid$newsid&Subject=New Generation for Forums"><img src="http://www.councilofarcana.com/news/envelope.gif" alt="E-mail New Generation for Forums" border=0></a> <a href="http://www.councilofarcana.com/news/viewnews.cgi?newsid$newsid" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.councilofarcana.com/news/printer.gif" alt="Print New Generation for Forums" border=0></a> </font><hr
                        size="1" color="#A8A8A8">
                        <font size="2"
                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">Last night, the Council of Arcana's Generation 2 Message Boards, which served us since early January of 2000, suffered a major functional crash. We decided, therefore, to implement a new long-term solution for our message boards needs, and have moved to Generation 3 Message Boards -- the ezBoards with which many of you have already become familiar. To access our new forums, please visit <b><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/bcouncilofarcana">this address</a></b>. Allanna and I have been laboring to get as much up and functional as possible, so, please remain patient and await further instructions on "the other side". ;-). Thanks!!</font>
