                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">In a stunning address before the General Assembly and the Committee on Newbie Events, Arch Chancellor Kaelon Xerxentis indicated that he would intervene on behalf of Senior Councilor Raevenn, and accept her resignation of her post of chair of Newbie Events, and empower her as an Adjutant of the Chancellory so that she has the flexibility and security so desired. Councilor Gabriale, subsequently, has been named as the new Senior Councilor of Review for the Committee on Newbie Events. Please <b><a href="http://www.councilofarcana.com/forum/Forum5/HTML/000014.html">read the address</a></b> for more.</font>
