                        <font size="2"
                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">Today, the Council of Arcana is holding two exciting events for members. The first is a <b><a href="http://www.alleria.com/council/forum/Forum2/HTML/000021.html">Raid on Castle Mistmoore</a></b>, open for levels 19 and higher. Objectives will be minimal -- lower-level players will remain in the courtyard, taking on familiars and initiates. Higher-level players will go into the chasm to retrieve an item for a quest. Depending upon attendance, we may or may not engage in a Castle incursion proper. The raid begins promptly at 6 pm Eastern Time, and ends at 9 pm Eastern Time. The second event is an <b>Officer Induction Ceremony</b> at The Lake Rathe Arena, at 10 PM Eastern Time, to be followed by friendly battles. All are invited.</font>
