                        <font size="2"
                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">The Guild Tag Bug, as many of you know, has returned in full force. The Guild Tag Bug occurs when you zone, crash, etc., and lose your guildtag and guildstatus. If this happens to you, please contact an officer (use our <b><a href="ledger.html">Council Ledger</a></b> to find an accurate listing), or fellow member to notify the Council. As Arch Chancellor, I will be designating additional temporary officers for the task of reguilding members that we drop. Thanks for your understanding, and make sure if you lose your guildtag to submit a /bug report.</font>
