                        size="1" color="#A8A8A8">
                        <font size="2"
                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">There were recently some questions and concerns regarding the Council of Arcana's acquisition of some of the members of the Order of Lightbringers. As Arch Chancellor, I have directly responded to some of these issues on my <a href="http://www.alleria.com/council/forum/Forum4/HTML/000006.html"><b>response to the OLB acquisition</b></a> which I encourage you to read if you have any thoughts on this issue. Ultimately, I mentioned that the Council agreed to admit a few initial members (Ailane, Menegorn and Thesidius), and then that all subsequent members would be considered using the procedures and regulations as stated in our <b><a href="about.html">guild documents</a></b>, stating specifically that no special treatment would be offered.</font>
