                        src="http://www.councilofarcana.com/forum/icons/icon1.gif"
                        width="15" height="15"> <font
                        color="#FFFFCC" size="1"
                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">posted
                        by <strong><a href="kaelon@alleria.com">Kaelon Xerxentis</a></strong> on
                        Wednesday, March 1, 2000 - 8:41 AM EST - <a href="http://www.councilofarcana.com/cgi-forum/ubbmisc.cgi?action=sendthread&thread=http://www.councilofarcana.com/news/viewnews.cgi?newsid$newsid&Subject=Norrathean Exchange Forum Up"><img src="http://www.councilofarcana.com/news/envelope.gif" alt="E-mail Norrathean Exchange Forum Up" border=0></a> <a href="http://www.councilofarcana.com/news/viewnews.cgi?newsid$newsid" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.councilofarcana.com/news/printer.gif" alt="Print Norrathean Exchange Forum Up" border=0></a> </font><hr
                        size="1" color="#A8A8A8">
                        <font size="2"
                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">Menegorn had suggested very wisely that the guild set-up a central place to discuss buying, selling, trading, exchanging, and Bazaar functions for our items. So, the <b><a href="http://www.alleria.com/council/cgi-forum/Ultimate.cgi">Council Chambers</a></b> now has a <b>Norrathean Exchange</b> forum up where you can discuss these issues. We encourage everyone to participate there if you are looking for that special item, or want to sell something to a fellow guild member. Please remember that trade in the guild should be standard, and uninflated.</font>
