                        size="1" color="#A8A8A8">
                        <font size="2"
                        face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">Ebane, a Cleric and one of the Original Founders of the Council of Arcana, has elected to leave our guild and join a smaller guild of personal friends. She made her announcement over guildchat today, and the High Council accepted her resignation and stripped her of her rank immediately thereafter. The Arch Chancellor called Ebane "one of the nicest, most honorable persons in Norrath" following her resignation, and said that the Council has lost a true asset. However, this decision was long in the planning and making, and did not come to a surprise, since Ebane had chosen to participate with a different group of friends months ago. We wish her the best.</font>
